{"tid":60101,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"女超人Melissa Benoist離婚","createTime":"2016-12-30T07:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T09:53:50.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cd8dd100aeccdefdc3669aa28226c4059058f3d9","tid":60101,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T07:32:46.000Z","msg":"雖然《女超人》（Supergirl）在移轉至CW電視網之後，依舊有著穩定的表現，不過飾演這位超級英雄的梅莉莎班諾伊（Melissa Benoist）卻在現實生活中面臨感情狀況，根據八卦媒體TMZ的報導，她已經向法院提出離婚。<br />\n<br />\n根據該媒體取得的法院文件，這位女演員以「不可調和的分歧」為理由申請離婚，並希望任何一方都無需給付贍養費，以及回復原本的名字，她與布萊克詹納（Blake Jenner）並未育有孩子。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩人因為合作《歡樂合唱團》（Glee）而開始交往，2013年7月訂婚，並在2015年7月踏上紅毯。婚後曾一起演出《超少女》，在接受國外媒體People的訪問時，梅莉莎班諾伊還曾表示：「我們一起工作時只有樂趣，他是與我一起演戲的人，也總是我最愛的螢幕夥伴。」<br />\n<br />\n兩人感情看起來一直十分融洽，不時會在社群網站分享合照，九月時為了支持布萊克的新作品《最佳閨蜜》（The Edge of Seventeen），也曾一同出席多倫多國際影展，如今看見他們走上離婚一途，相信會讓不少支持她們的粉絲感到有些難過。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://images.celebritymoviearchive.com/members/thumbs/hd/m/5991/Melissa%20Benoist%20%26%20Brianna%20Brown%20-%20Homeland%20-%20S01E02%20-%20BD_3-500.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.celebritymoviearchive.com%2Fmembers%2Fthumbs%2Fhd%2Fm%2F5991%2FMelissa%2520Benoist%2520%2526%2520Brianna%2520Brown%2520-%2520Homeland%2520-%2520S01E02%2520-%2520BD_3-500.jpg&d=XkRSC%2FEfHioiJMa4qxcPepkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=efd1f062\" target=\"_blank\">http://images.celebritymoviearchive.com/members/thumbs/hd/m/5991/Melissa%20Benoist%20%26%20Brianna%20Brown%20-%20Homeland%20-%20S01E02%20-%20BD_3-500.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n會唔會有新相流出架"},{"pid":"db335a5a1a02cf6a6f17a489583f0411824b808d","tid":60101,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T09:01:54.000Z","msg":"好撚正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9a70855510eedd4d7e68a669104c3e9344cae8","tid":60101,"uid":24739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T16:22:03.000Z","msg":"竟然離婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b5acb4cb2901a729a6eea74405c80b18fc2fe70","tid":60101,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T09:53:50.000Z","msg":"佢啲流出相好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}